Pursuant to Rule 42(a)(2), the Court appoints the United States Attorneys Office of the Southern District of California, Criminal Division and the designated Assistant United States Attorney to prosecute the contempt. A first appearance in the above-entitled action has been placed on the calendar of the Honorable John A. Houston on September 21, 2018 at 11:30 a.m., in Courtroom 13B.
